title: Tristan Thompson declines qualifying offer, remains a restricted free agent
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Cavaliers - Today 
Tristan Thompson elected to let the Cleveland Cavaliers' qualifying offer deadline pass and he remains a restricted free agent....
